Your group project is due soon. One classmate has gone quiet, another is trying to take over, and the work still needs to get done.

-> Reassign the work and set a deadline. #choice:reassign_the_work
    You divide what remains, name an owner for each piece, and set one last deadline.
    <<stim_resolve_choice "school_group_project_politics_001" "reassign_the_work">>
