-> Do the missing work yourself. #choice:do_it_yourself
    You open the unfinished sections and start filling the gaps alone.
    <<stim_resolve_choice "school_group_project_politics_001" "do_it_yourself">>
    <<stop>>
-> Tell the teacher exactly what happened. #choice:tell_the_teacher
    You explain who completed what and ask the teacher to step in.
    <<stim_resolve_choice "school_group_project_politics_001" "tell_the_teacher">>
